| [[w:IPA|IPA]] || /æbˈsɛn(t)ʃiə/,  /æbˈsɛn(t)ʃə/
|-
| [[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]] || /{b"sEn(t)Si@/, /{b"sEn(t)S@/
|}

===Noun===
'''absentia'''
# [[absence]]

===Usage note===
Only in the phrase '''[[in absentia]]''' .

